UNITED STATES of America ex rel. Joseph H. PETERS, Appellant, v. Stanley P. ASHE, Warden, Western State Penitentiary, Pittsburgh, Pa. No. 9225. Circuit Court of Appeals, Third Circuit. Submitted on Briefs Jan. 6, 1947. Decided Jan. 10, 1947. Joseph H. Peters, in pro. per. John E. Stevenson, Sp. Deputy Atty. Gen., for appellee.

Before BIGGS, McLAUGHLIN, and KALODNER, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The order of the court below is affirmed.
